PokemonLeague_LancesRoom_Text_Intro::
    .string "Lance: I've been waiting for \n"
	.string "you {PLAYER}.\p"
	.string "I knew that you, with your skills,\n"
	.string "would eventually reach me here.\p"
	.string "There's no need for words now.\p"
	.string "We will battle to determine who is\n"
	.string "the stronger of the two of us.\p"
	.string "As the most powerful Trainer\n"
	.string "and as the Pokémon League Champion…\p"
	.string "I, Lance the dragon master,\n"
	.string "accept your challenge!$"

PokemonLeague_LancesRoom_Text_RematchIntro::
    .string "Ah!\n"
    .string "So, you've returned, Paul!\p"
    .string "I lead the ELITE FOUR.\p"
    .string "You can call me LANCE the dragon\n"
    .string "TRAINER.\p"
    .string "You know that dragons are\n"
    .string "mythical POKéMON.\p"
    .string "They're hard to catch and raise,\n"
    .string "but their powers are superior.\p"
    .string "They're virtually indestructible.\n"
    .string "There's no being clever with them.\p"
    .string "Well, are you ready to lose?\p"
    .string "Your LEAGUE challenge ends with\n"
    .string "me, Paul!{PLAY_BGM}{MUS_ENCOUNTER_GYM_LEADER}$"

PokemonLeague_LancesRoom_Text_Defeat::
    .string "…It's over\p"
	.string "But it's an odd feeling.\n"
	.string "I'm not angry that I lost.\l"
	.string "In fact, I feel happy.\p"
	.string "Happy that I witnessed the rise\n"
	.string "of a great new Champion!$"

PokemonLeague_LancesRoom_Text_PostBattle::
    .string "Lance: …Whew. You have become\n"
	.string "truly powerful {PLAYER}{KUN}.\p"
	.string "Your Pokémon have responded to your\n"
	.string "strong and upstanding nature.\p"
	.string "As a Trainer, you will continue\n"
	.string "to grow strong with your POKéMON.$"
